lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F073302_0f7d6bb5151b37d41fbb2efc4ce15f1c.jpg&h=ae7299af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最正既沙律吧 無限芝士粉 麵包糠 香蒜蕃茄汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過就咁食沙律吧加甜品吧 都要成128加一...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/073304_fd018d1f843708f455ead12e1800390e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F073304_fd018d1f843708f455ead12e1800390e.jpg&h=c56bf902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個就豬肋骨 無咩特別 m記bbq醬味...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/073305_e8e93cbe7ad83f5bba035e650825b9eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F073305_e8e93cbe7ad83f5bba035e650825b9eb.jpg&h=e9bae75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢碟搵笨 238加一 <br />\n羊架肉質比一般放題好<br />\n牛扒...ruby tuesday質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒春雞 真係夠春 細到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個汁先難食...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結 淨食沙津吧 都抵食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[/member</blockquote><br />\ndie 分享"}]}